.. code:: console

   $ freshbugs --help
   usage: freshbugs [-h] [--dry-run] [--clean] [--all] REQUEST [REQUEST ...]

   positional arguments:
     REQUEST     either a bug number or an e-mail address

   optional arguments:
     -h, --help  show this help message and exit
     --dry-run   make cache read-only
     --clean     remove old items from cache
     --all       print all selected bugs' details

